WeibullR.plotly 0.3

Source: news.md
  • Now with support for Reliability Growth Analysis via the plotly_duane and plotly_rga functions.
  • New vignettes on Weibull Analysis and Reliability Growth Analysis.
  • Other minor improvements and bug fixes.
